-- Popular in talks to buy Citibank's retail business in Spain 
-- 
-- Fri Apr 04, 2014 03:03AM EDT
-- None



MADRID, April 4 (Reuters) - Spanish lender Banco Popular <POP.MC> said on Friday that it is in talks to buy Citibank's <C.N> retail banking and credit card business in Spain but did not provide any financial details.

